snippet.title: You'll be SURPRISED that SQUIRRELS CAN BE FUNNIER THAN CATS - Funny ANIMAL compilation
snippet.description:

Just look how all these funny little creatures! behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute!
